{"tid":785133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推友人落橋飛墮18米全身重創 少女遭起訴恐踎監","createTime":"2018-08-19T03:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T05:02:35.000Z","uid":80516,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"75a43c0b475c7e8ef7e2dd6a2077c2e2e60720fd","tid":785133,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:07:44.000Z","msg":"美國華盛頓州16歲少女霍奇森（Jordan Holgerson），本月初遭18歲友人史密斯（Taylor Smith）推落橋，由18米高處墮河，身受重創。史密斯上周五（17日）被控魯莽危害他人罪，<span style=\"color: red;\">一旦罪成最高判囚一年</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ；惟霍奇森希望當局加重控罪。<br />\n<br />\n霍奇森本月7日到亞科爾特（Yacolt）劉易斯河一條橋玩跳水，當她猶豫不決之際，突然被史密斯從後推下。直插河中的霍奇森合共有5條肋骨骨折，肺部及全身多處損傷，需數個月才能康復。<br />\n<br />\n經剪接的跳水片在網上瘋傳，史密斯承認推霍奇森下河，但辯稱是霍奇森要求，自己只是助她「克服恐懼」。惟當地電視台取得的完整片段顯示，霍奇森多次大叫「不要」，又要求史密斯15分鐘後再推她下水。<br />\n<br />\n史密斯被控魯莽危害他人罪；惟在家休養的霍奇森質疑控罪過輕，不足以令對方明白所犯過錯，要求檢方加重控罪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/irrCOjLSGwEYnUNB6izvtw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIwO2g9MzUw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/a499cb1e616fc340c5412dd2f80e0a13\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FirrCOjLSGwEYnUNB6izvtw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIwO2g9MzUw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fa499cb1e616fc340c5412dd2f80e0a13&h=b1c8674f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20180819/photo/bkn-20180819060053063-0819_00972_001_01b.jpg?20180819080643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20180819%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180819060053063-0819_00972_001_01b.jpg%3F20180819080643&h=324f8ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20180819/photo/bkn-20180819060053063-0819_00972_001_02b.jpg?20180819080643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20180819%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180819060053063-0819_00972_001_02b.jpg%3F20180819080643&h=6a5125c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20180819/bkn-20180819060053063-0819_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20180819%2Fbkn-20180819060053063-0819_00972_001.html&d=AIqUl6y7bt%2B40G6QuTLocAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3530f8d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20180819/bkn-20180819060053063-0819_00972_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a32285a04618651df64dea3c8134f253296b880d","tid":785133,"uid":86756,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56a0c248c711804a5bf644bace715ae2d2ac33b","tid":785133,"uid":18669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:18:23.000Z","msg":"推人果條女手臂粗撚到.."},{"pid":"d4aa93d833e33b0e6c9abfd56cf7fd8deef51248","tid":785133,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:19:59.000Z","msg":"唔係判左坐一年喇咩"},{"pid":"d0d92eefb007e29d5210b05ecd8666850347d017","tid":785133,"uid":132587,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"女人友誼就好似跳海條女d肋骨一樣咁脆弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded7781ad0c1bec64655800f88f52b48266c32ef","tid":785133,"uid":166725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:24:36.000Z","msg":"其實兩者之間係咪有咩感情糾紛？"},{"pid":"87a85558d4783259356d3969d518153a1eefe4c4","tid":785133,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"冇人blame the victim?<br />\n如果條女自己唔係坐喺橋邊會有人推到佢？"},{"pid":"cf3142dca32d3bb43acd198ab8af27720c013350","tid":785133,"uid":19124,"like":